{"tid":1700402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港人等夠拖捨未？」由林奠笑住為死左消防員追授勳章，到今日甴曱隊係鏡頭前貓哭老鼠","createTime":"2019-11-08T13:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T14:25:32.000Z","uid":81236,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88a8c106382fde1ef0d0001e68d0a9bf86d697e4","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.litenews.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/lam-cheng_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.litenews.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Flam-cheng_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.png&h=b9212f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本就係如出一轍<br />\n<br />\n仲有無數咁多人裸屍被跳樓被浮海<br />\n<br />\n然而居然仲有一堆人希望政府放香港人一條生路<br />\n<br />\n仲被動咁希望政府/甴曱隊有一日會查明真相，還香港人公義<br />\n<br />\n如果你係既，你簡直豬狗不如<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你只係消費緊香港死去既義士黎希望換取極權拖捨既一點回報</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n極權、曱甴隊、保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n出賣盡香港人利益<br />\n就算香港人死哂佢地都唔會覺得可惜<br />\n唔會為香港人留一點憐憫<br />\n<br />\n根本唔配做一個香港人"},{"pid":"0d9c548d08cf8775adad37797e352f9284905eec","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9291862d9b521313245568c451b8d44080ed5ad0","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a66d942aebe4f6d83b82d6c97a03ad562bb35651","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:49:23.000Z","msg":"Psuh"},{"pid":"d103f6e3ffce623ae89ffd6f260395b13fc87525","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8923b5fab43272627abb2ecd07227f0ecac5d117","tid":1700402,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:49:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e88969c139f675cb83b0e5ade4a338dcd69